<lb n="0285a16" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0285a17" ed="T"/><cb:docNumber>No. 1258</cb:docNumber><cb:div type="jing">
<lb n="0285a18" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><note n="0285001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】享保年間刊豐山大學藏本，【甲】保延三年寫高山寺藏本，【乙】保安四年寫寶壽院藏本</note>摩利支菩薩略念誦法</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0285a19" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0285a20" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator">大興善寺三藏沙門大廣智
<lb n="0285a21" ed="T"/>不空奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0285a22" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0285a2201">先應結毘盧遮那佛印。</p>
<lb n="0285a23" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0285a2301"><note n="0285002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">次＝其【甲】</note><note n="0285002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">次【大】，其【甲】</note><app n="0285002"><lem wit="【大】">次</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">其</rdg></app>印相者。二手內相叉。並竪二大指即成。
<lb n="0285a24" ed="T"/>誦真言七遍頂上散。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0285a25" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0285a2501" cb:type="dharani">曩莫三滿多沒馱南阿尾羅吽<note n="0285003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">欠＋（平呼）細註【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0285003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">欠【大】，欠(平呼)【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0285003"><lem wit="【大】">欠</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">欠<note place="inline">平呼</note></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0285a26" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0285a2601">次結摩利支菩薩根本真言印。</p>
<lb n="0285a27" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0285a2701">次印相者。以二手內相叉。竪合二頭指。二中
<lb n="0285a28" ed="T"/>指<note n="0285004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（相）＋各【甲】</note><note n="0285004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">各【大】，相各【甲】</note><app n="0285004"><lem wit="【大】">各</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">相各</rdg></app>糺持二頭指令相捻。二大指並竪合即
<lb n="0285a29" ed="T"/>成。誦真言加持身五處。印額次右肩次左肩。</p>
<pb n="0285b" xml:id="T21.1258.0285b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0285b01" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0285b0101">次心<note n="0285005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔次〕－【乙】</note><note n="0285005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">次【大】，〔－〕【乙】</note><app n="0285005"><lem wit="【大】">次</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>喉上。以各誦一遍。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0285b02" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0285b0201" cb:type="dharani">曩謨<note place="inline">引</note>囉怛曩<note place="inline">二合</note>怛囉<note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0285006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">夜＋（引）夾註【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0285006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">夜【大】，夜(引)【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0285006"><lem wit="【大】">夜</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">夜<note place="inline">引</note></rdg></app>耶<note place="inline">一</note>怛儞也<note place="inline">二
<lb n="0285b03" ed="T"/>合</note>他<note place="inline">引二</note>遏迦沫思<note place="inline">三</note>沫迦沫<note n="0285007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">思＝惡【乙】</note><note n="0285007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">思【大】，惡【乙】</note><app n="0285007"><lem wit="【大】">思</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">惡</rdg></app>遏度<note place="inline">引</note>沫思<note place="inline">四</note>
<lb n="0285b04" ed="T"/>旨跛囉沫思<note place="inline">五</note><note n="0285008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">摩＝度【甲】</note><note n="0285008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">摩【大】，度【甲】</note><app n="0285008"><lem wit="【大】">摩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">度</rdg></app>賀<note place="inline">引</note>旨跛囉沫思<note place="inline">六</note>按怛
<lb n="0285b05" ed="T"/><note n="0285009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">馱＝但【乙】</note><note n="0285009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">馱【大】，但【乙】</note><app n="0285009"><lem wit="【大】">馱</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">但</rdg></app>娜沫思<note place="inline">七</note>摩哩制野沫思<note place="inline">八</note>曩謨薩都<note place="inline">二合</note>
<lb n="0285b06" ed="T"/>帝<note place="inline">九</note>𡀩乞叉<note place="inline">二合</note>𡀩乞叉<note place="inline">二合</note>𤚥<note place="inline">引十</note>薩嚩薩怛
<lb n="0285b07" ed="T"/>嚩<note place="inline">二合</note>難<note place="inline">引</note>者<note place="inline">十一</note>薩嚩怛囉<note place="inline">二合</note>薩嚩<note n="0285010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">波＝婆【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0285010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">波【大】，婆【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0285010"><lem wit="【大】">波</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">婆</rdg></app>庾<note place="inline">引十
<lb n="0285b08" ed="T"/>二</note>跛捺囉<note place="inline">二合</note>吠毘藥<note place="inline">二合</note>娑嚩<note n="0285011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">二合＝引二合【甲】，二合引【乙】</note><note n="0285011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">二合【大】，引二合【甲】，二合引【乙】</note><app n="0285011"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><note place="inline">引二合</note></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】"><note place="inline">二合引</note></rdg></app>訶<note n="0285012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔引十三〕－【甲】</note><note n="0285012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">引十三【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0285012"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引十三</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0285b09" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0285b0901">次結摩利支菩薩心印。真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0285b10" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0285b1001" cb:type="dharani">曩莫三滿多沒馱<note place="inline">引</note>南<note n="0285013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔引〕－【甲】</note><note n="0285013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">引【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0285013"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>唵摩<note place="inline">引</note><note n="0285014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔利〕－【甲】</note><note n="0285014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">利【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0285014"><lem wit="【大】">利</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>哩制曳
<lb n="0285b11" ed="T"/><note n="0285015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">沙嚩二合＝二合娑婆【甲】</note><note n="0285015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">沙嚩二合【大】，二合娑婆【甲】</note><app n="0285015"><lem wit="【大】">沙嚩<note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">二合娑婆</rdg></app><note n="0285016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">訶＋（引）夾註【乙】</note><note n="0285016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">訶【大】，訶(引)【乙】</note><app n="0285016"><lem wit="【大】">訶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">訶<note place="inline">引</note></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0285b12" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0285b1201"><note n="0285017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">次＝心【乙】</note><note n="0285017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">次【大】，心【乙】</note><app n="0285017"><lem wit="【大】">次</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">心</rdg></app>結<note n="0285018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">心＋（印）【甲】</note><note n="0285018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">心【大】，心印【甲】</note><app n="0285018"><lem wit="【大】">心</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">心印</rdg></app>真言印相者。以左手虛作拳。頭指
<lb n="0285b13" ed="T"/>大母指相捻如環。想自身入左<note n="0285019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔手〕－【甲】</note><note n="0285019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">手【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0285019"><lem wit="【大】">手</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>拳中。以右
<lb n="0285b14" ed="T"/>手覆左拳上。即想此印為摩利支菩薩形。想
<lb n="0285b15" ed="T"/>自身<note n="0285020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（隱）＋在【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0285020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">在【大】，隱在【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0285020"><lem wit="【大】">在</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">隱在</rdg></app>摩利支菩薩心中不斷絕。誦身真言
<lb n="0285b16" ed="T"/>應時獲得殊勝加持。不被一切惡人為障礙
<lb n="0285b17" ed="T"/>者所見。一切災禍皆不著身。一切口舌皆得
<lb n="0285b18" ed="T"/><note n="0285021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">除＝消【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0285021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">除【大】，消【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0285021"><lem wit="【大】">除</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">消</rdg></app>滅。蟲狼虎豹水火盜<note n="0285022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔則〕－【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0285022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">則【大】，〔－〕【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0285022"><lem wit="【大】">則</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>賊皆不能侵害。
<lb n="0285b19" ed="T"/>所求世間果報皆得諧偶。若修出世間法。<note n="0285023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">即＝速【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0285023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">即【大】，速【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0285023"><lem wit="【大】">即</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">速</rdg></app>
<lb n="0285b20" ed="T"/>得禪定現前。智慧增盛獲得聞持。不忘失菩
<lb n="0285b21" ed="T"/>提心法。誦真言時深起<note n="0285024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">悲愍＝慈悲【甲】</note><note n="0285024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">悲愍【大】，慈悲【甲】</note><app n="0285024"><lem wit="【大】">悲愍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">慈悲</rdg></app>。為一切有情拔
<lb n="0285b22" ed="T"/>除苦惱。皆獲無障解脫速證無上菩提道。應
<lb n="0285b23" ed="T"/>須祕密勿<note n="0285025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">妄＝忘【甲】</note><note n="0285025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">妄【大】，忘【甲】</note><app n="0285025"><lem wit="【大】">妄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">忘</rdg></app>傳授。</p>
<lb n="0285b24" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="close"><cb:jhead>摩利支菩薩略念誦<note n="0285026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">此下甲本奧書曰保延三年二月二十五日酉尅書畢執筆生年二十歲□□□保延三年五月十四日辰時交點了，乙本奧書曰保安四年四月十六日書了同日移點了執筆<g ref="#SD-B577"/></note>法</cb:jhead></cb:juan></cb:div>
</body></text></TEI>